div.p: This document servers the purpose to describe the technical,

technical details around the operation of the KeysFortress cloud used with the Frontend software (Mobile,Desktop or Tablet) in relation to the
The personal cloud is designed as the name implies, personal use, so it doesn't include any of the enterprise features that the proprietary version of KeysFortress supports.

div.div:
We want to keep it as simple as possible, therefore we decided to stick with the same tech stack across both the propriatary and personal cloud so it goes as follows. We do recodnize that some of the choices might not be the first choice of new developers, however we use the tools that our team is familiar with over personal preferences.
- Web platform - Angular 17.0 (Web Platform)
- Api - GOLANG (API)
- CLI - GOLANG (CLI)
